@node Main "Midnight Blanker Document"

  Randomly chooses your modules.  This user friendly module will

  allow you to select and deselect modules for inclusion into a

  group of modules which will be randomly choosen for screen

  saving.


  @{"Editor Options" link Options}

  Ę Do NOT change the name of this blanker
    module.  Its operation is depended on
    its name being correct!


