@endnode


@node Options "Editor Options"

  Name          HotKey    Description
  -----------------------------------
  UP/DOWN ARROW           Selects modules.
  LEFT/RIGHT ARROW        Chooses module for inclusion or exclusion.

  Exclude       E         If checked, those modules selected will not be
                          choosen for screen saving.
  
  Save          S         Saves preferences.
  Cancel        C         Exit/Cancel without saving.

@endnode
